[[File:Hollowtown.jpg|thumb|right|250px|The Glowpoint devastating Hollowtown during the firing of Centerpoint's Starbuster]]

The '''Glowpoint''' was a large, [[Star/Legends|star]]-like [[Reactor/Legends|reactor]] that supplied power to the [[Centerpoint Station]]. It was an artificial sun that was suspended in the exact center of the sphere; unbeknownst to those living in the settlement of [[Hollowtown]] around the star, Glowpoint was in essence a pilot light&mdash;it served to maintain the station's power supply and would generate an immense flare when the station was used. To simulate night, farmers installed adjustable [[shadow-shields]], which appeared as bright patches of gold or silver from above.

On both sides of the [[Hollowtown]] sphere, positioned along the spin axis, was a large cone ringed by six smaller cones; the sets were called the North and South Conical Mountains.

